# CLIENT + MTK-REQUEST REBUILD PROMPT
# All files live in client/ (no subdirectories)
# Load order in index.html: client.js THEN wc-include(client.html)
# client.html loads: mtk-request.config.js → mtk-request.js → client.config.js

---

## client/index.html

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>Client</title>
        <base href="/repo_deploy/">
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <script>
         wcENV="dev";
         wcAPP="app";
         wcURL="";
        </script>
        <link href="vendor/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="vendor/css/material-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="vendor/css/font-awesome.all.min.css">
        <link href="css/fonts/fonts.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="css/nala.css" rel="stylesheet">
    </head>
    <body id="wc">
        <script src="vendor/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="vendor/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        <script src="js/_wc.js"></script>
        <script src="js/app.js"></script>
        <script src="js/_febe.js" defer></script>

        <!-- CLIENT: client.js MUST load before wc-include so window.client() is defined -->
        <script src="client/client.js"></script>
        <div style="border:2px red dashed">
            <link href="client/client.css" rel="stylesheet">
            <wc-include href="client/client.html"/>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
```

