## client/mtk-request.scss

```scss
.mtk-request {

  display: block;

  .modal-dialog {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .modal-dialog {
      max-width: 95%;
    }
  }

  .md-field {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .md-field input,
  .md-field textarea,
  .md-field select {
    width: 100%;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #ccc;
    padding: 10px 0 6px;
    background: transparent;
    outline: none;
  }

  .md-field label {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #777;
    transition: 0.2s;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .md-field.active label,
  .md-field input:focus + label,
  .md-field textarea:focus + label,
  .md-field select:focus + label {
    top: -10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #0d6efd;
  }

  .contact-group {
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .group-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #777;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .radio-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .radio-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .radio-item input {
    display: none;
  }

  .radio-custom {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border: 2px solid #777;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .radio-item input:checked + .radio-custom {
    border-color: #0d6efd;
  }

  .radio-item input:checked + .radio-custom::after {
    content: "";
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: #0d6efd;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    top: 2px;
    left: 2px;
  }

  .phone-times {
    display: none;
  }

  .phone-times.active {
    display: block;
  }

  .submit-wrap {
    text-align: right;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .submit-btn {
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    width: auto;
  }

  :focus {
    outline: 2px solid #0d6efd;
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
}

// Placeholder styling
.mtk-request .md-field {
  input::placeholder,
  textarea::placeholder {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #bbb;
  }
}
```

---

## KEY RULES (do not break these)

1. **client.js loads BEFORE wc-include** in index.html — defines `var client = window.client`
2. **client.config.js loads INSIDE client.html** (last script) — calls `client({...})`
3. **mtk-request dialog is inlined in client.html** — no nested wc-include (jQuery doesn't trigger connectedCallback on injected custom elements)
4. **MtkRequest is guarded** with `if (typeof MtkRequest === 'undefined')` to prevent duplicate class declaration on re-load
5. **nalaUID flow**: config → btnEstimate click sets hidden `.nala-uid` input → submit reads it → published in payload
6. **Validation order**: name → contact-type-driven required → OR required → format → help
7. **SCSS only** — never edit the compiled .css directly
